His dance was sensual and I was told that my dance is also within this aesthetic, "he says.
The assembly has two exceptional collaborations: that of Miguel Poveda who will sing again to Isabel in one in his shows, as he did in the "The Open Door"; and with the teacher Matilde Coral, who has exceptionally wanted to collaborate with whoever was her student.
"Matilde makes Tortola the oldest, the character of maturity.
I am happy that I have agreed to act in my work and I am very honored by it. "
