In most cases rather the potential represented by the company is what can be fearful and not remorse, fear for punishment, yearning for freedom or rebellion against power.
However, it is already confirmed that not only do they retain, but in justifiable cases they also give to third parties all the expressions sought, in these cases there is nothing to protect the personal rights of netizens.
