A normal young man can have a profile on many collective pages, from Facebook to Xanga, and can even join them with other services, such as Twitter or the last.fm that offers a list of his music customs, then they can be included in a follow-up system such as the FriendFeed or the Blip.fm, you can also have a blog, which automatically features the latest photo galleries that are stored in the Flickr or the Picasa.
