One of the company's internal regulations says that they will not announce any new service in advance, but only when it is ready to work, what if it is certain is that the foreseeable problems of the coming months and years will be able to stir up the world: while some believe that the Google project of scanning and archiving books and magazines will acquire such dimensions that the company will soon be quoted by the United States Supreme Court, others fear of their health system, because in it we can create our own complete health profile, with previous analysis, with our doctors and our problems.
